This is a list of U.S. Vice Presidents by date of birth .
List of United States Vice Presidents by date of birth
List of United States Vice Presidents by date of birth
Between the births of John Adams in 1735 and Al Gore in 1948, a vice president has been born in every decade except the 1760s , 1890s and 1930s .
